{"tid":1301190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家睇下呢條台灣講現時香港局勢嘅片","createTime":"2019-07-09T14:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T15:29:22.000Z","uid":51525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"63396cd4b73cb2be78431c3515a12d220487a4bc","tid":1301190,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RzOwobCxnHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRzOwobCxnHk&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=793b06a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RzOwobCxnHk</a><br />\n希望大家抽時間睇一睇<br />\n我想大家知道<br />\n其實世界上有好多人係支持我地<br />\n因為民主同自由係普世價值 全世界都認同嘅一件事<br />\n呢條係台灣人整嘅一條片 略略講下香港由回歸到而家嘅局勢<br />\n希望大家睇完可以重拾心情 再繼續努力<br />\n香港人 加油<br />\n<br />\n條片到最後 佢講左幾句 我想引用俾大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人一直告訴我們 請踏在香港的屍體上 想台灣的道路<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可是我們更想跟香港人說 讓我們一起共同尋找<br />\n一個沒有中共威權獨裁打壓的幸福可能</span></span>"},{"pid":"ae415bce1e4a2009fa7986e456688c029cd67bb7","tid":1301190,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:45:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我無嘢講"},{"pid":"2ebaa8a2268b8d512a0aa0919f1bce4fc10b9e77","tid":1301190,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我要去醫院"},{"pid":"3e8021dc2f852f90901364ae901c563768ca1904","tid":1301190,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:14:15.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我要見律師"},{"pid":"dfb085038e16a1de417bb65cac3a943d0db2e032","tid":1301190,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:29:22.000Z","msg":"推"}]}